{"tid":1602512,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警禮頓道推進 已制服情況下仍以警棍追打至少三下","createTime":"2019-09-29T12:15:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T13:00:56.000Z","uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"118aa80f768348a76326fc1f22443c67af8a6650","tid":1602512,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:15:57.000Z","msg":"(19:43) 入夜後，近千示威者向銅鑼灣方向撤退，警方在多條街道佈防，並一度在恩平道發射催淚彈。<br />\n<br />\n部份示威者在紀利華木球會外聚集，防暴警察則在禮頓道、香港電訊東區電訊大廈外設立防線，發射數枚催淚彈後向摩理臣山道快速推進。有警員在已制伏的示威者的情況下，仍以警棍追打示威者至少三下。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1067543\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1067543&d=AXXoxpexL8qkFRpCGxAvLcFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=001e34d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1067543&h=50e68faa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1067543</a>"},{"pid":"042e4688d36026d9bd7d0eb4ca1de64dd853b45e","tid":1602512,"uid":312412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:00:56.000Z","msg":"[twitter懶人包]全部同我入泥！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1602587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1602587</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}